$ PowerShell module outlook: save-outlookMails
@ save-outlookMails

`save-outlookMails` (of the Powershell Module → Windows/PowerShell/modules/personal/Outlook[Outlook]) uses `→ Windows/PowerShell/modules/personal/Outlook/invoke-scriptBlockOnOutlookMails` to
save all mails in the inbox and the sent folder.

